(I'll soon rectify myself of having 9 Alliance members soon, I don't feel 
comfortable with having them just poof into thin air)

Punch/Jaws/The Oblitercons/Nemesis Enforcer/Scattershot:




Punch slowly got out of his recharge bed and stretched his mechanical limbs 
and left his quarters, heading for the bridge of the Alliance base, ready for 
his shift.

---

Jaws lay floating halfway above water near the shields of the Alliance 
Island, in a sleep mode and slowly regaining energy lost to fighting against 
the current of the waters surrounding him.

---

The Oblitercons rested in a CR chamber inside the Alliance base, their bad 
wounds slowly being repaired as if they never existed.

---

Scattershot laughed, pointing to the bubbling CR pool near his feet that held 
Nemesis Enforcer.  "Retard." he chuckled, leaving the CR room and heading for 
his quarters.
